bad economic news, including higher inflation, rising interest
rates, and threats of a dockworkers' strike.
   Mrs. Thatcher will celebrate her 10th anniversary in power May 4.
   The newspaper did not say when the poll was conducted, how many
people were questioned, or what the margin of error was.
